metadata.name: The Gentle Giant
metadata.description:
Take a break from the chaos of the NFT world and join the human friends and their giant companion as they embark on peaceful outdoor activities. The soothing color palette and the peaceful scenes depicted in each artwork create a sense of calm and tranquility, reminding the viewer to take a moment to relax and unwind. 

Amidst the hustle and bustle of the virtual world, there is still beauty and peace to be found in nature and in the simple things. üê≥

Tools: chatGPT, Midjourney, GIMP, Topaz Gigapixel AI.
